&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Central Administration Team Leader&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enki Medical Practice is looking for a Central Administration Team Leader, to supervise all Medical Secretaries and Document Management Administrators within the team, working with the Central Administration Manager to plan work on a day-to-day basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This requires regular reviews with the administrative processes and protocols within the team and ensure these are continuously improved to ensure delivery of a high quality service. The ideal candidate will be a Team Leader with experience and a key interest in team management. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel that you can lead a team positively by encouraging team work, development and growth this role may be the one for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion about the role please contact Suzanna Ball, Central Administration Manager via e-mail address suzanna.ball@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date for applications is Monday 9th October 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
